            <font class=newstitle>Trakanon begin to cast a gate spell.</font><br><br>
            <font class=newsitem>Oh yeah the story of Trakanon ! How we failed ? Some god was watching over Trakanon shoulder last night on our first attempt. Not only he gated once, but twice, nah not twice, he gated three times before he eventually won the hmmm very owned and long battle ? :)<br><br>I believe we did around 42k-44k damages last night on the first Trakanon. Since at his first gate from the lair in the back he gained around 20%hp, then he started to run (yes i didnt know trakanon was running away) to the bridge, then at the bridge (owned again). The sob regated to this lair, we runned back, recharged for the 3rd times (he was at 20%hp again from the second gate).... Then i falled around 10-15%, but when he got at 5% he started to whack peoples left and right and gated back in his spot. Sad story ? <br><br>NAH ! I never post sad story, we summoned corpses. Then the rage was in the air... The frustation was non-stop. From zone in to Trakanon dead we took 45 minutes total. I think juggs never got scared so much in they life ;)<br><br>Congrats on the kill, Trakanon was full of phat lewt (at least not a rogue BP and a ranger BP hehe).<br><br>Screenshot of the dead thing :<br><a href="http://www3.sympatico.ca/colsen/news/news10-trakanon.jpg"><img src="http://www3.sympatico.ca/colsen/news/news10-trakanon-300.jpg" BORDER=0 ALIGN=LEFT></a>Lewt :<br>Daakkon: <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=2059" target="_null">Deepwater Breastplate</a><br>Chamsie: <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=2117" target="_null">Manna Robe</a><br>Blarg : <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=587" target="_null">Trakanon's Tooth</a><br>Nickson : <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=587" target="_null">Trakanon's Tooth</a><br>Gomorrha : <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=587" target="_null">Trakanon's Tooth</a><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>We couldn't finish the night like that, of course not ! We heard that Talendor was up... looked an easy task for us, since we owned Trakanon really bad 2 times hehe. Well that was not, actually we failed twice when Talendor was at 1%hp. I think the first time Talendor was walking away with 100hp-200hp when we failed.... Similar the second time...<br><br>But, no bed for us until revenge !! Talendor falled on our 3rd try ! Was a long night, but rewards was there :)<br><br>Talendor incoming #2 by Balise :<br><a href="http://www3.sympatico.ca/colsen/news/news10-tal.jpg"><img src="http://www3.sympatico.ca/colsen/news/news10-tal-300.jpg" BORDER=0></a><br><br><img src="http://www3.sympatico.ca/colsen/news/news10-talloot.jpg" BORDER=0 align=left>Lewt : <br>Daakkon (yeah him again) : <a href=" http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=6123" target="_null">Torn Burnt Book</a><br>Kamandar : <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=1593" target="_null">Gauntlets of Fiery Might</a><br>Akuk (UF) : <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=3226" target="_null">Red Dragon Scale</a><br>Monev : <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=2592" target="_null">Kayruul's Mystic Pouch</a><br><br>Spells :<br>Euni (NC) : <a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/spells/spell.asp?Id=661" target="_null">Vengeance of Al'Kabor</a><br>Blarg: <a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/spells/spell.asp?Id=1768" target="_null">Avatar</a><br>Balise: <a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/spells/spell.asp?Id=983" target="_null">Form of the Hunter</a><br>Gordron: <a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/spells/spell.asp?Id=799" target="_null">Aegis</a><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>MORE, MORE, MORE !<br><br>Big big night, very big i tell you, not only we owned 2 dragons but Kttii completed his new <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=6355" target="_null">Crazy Cleric Breastplate</a> ! Congrats Kttii on the very hard work ! (its a lots of work believe me).<br><br>Stat: 60 AC +5 Str +5 Sta +15 Wis +10 vsMg +5 vsPos +5 vsDis +40 HP +90 Mana +6.00 Wt<br><br>On him :<br><a href="http://www3.sympatico.ca/colsen/news/news10-kttii1.jpg"><img src="http://www3.sympatico.ca/colsen/news/news10-kttii1-300.jpg" BORDER=0></a><a href="http://www3.sympatico.ca/colsen/news/news10-kttii2.jpg"><img src="http://www3.sympatico.ca/colsen/news/news10-kttii2-300.jpg" BORDER=0></a><br></font><br><br>
